Loretta Lynn’s Ranch and the Waverly, Tennessee community have graciously hosted the Fox Amateur Team for decades. Providing our Brand and Riders a platform to showcase their talents and create lasting memories both on and off the track. 

We were devastated to hear of the recent floods that took place and our thoughts are with all of those effected. Fox Racing is proud to support Racers 4 Waverly to help rebuild this special place for all of us.

Click the link in our bio to support the cause and look for a charity Auction coming soon! #foxracing #racers4waverly @road2recovery
